text: The Cut River may refer to one of the following rivers: *Cut River (Mackinac County, Michigan), a river in the Upper Peninsula of Michigan **Cut River Bridge, carries U.S. Route 2 over the Cut River *Cut River (Roscommon County, Michigan), a river in the Lower Peninsula of Michigan *Cuț River, a tributary of the Tazlăul Sărat in Romania
title: Cut River
